<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>B2B Lead Gen</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1a365d 0%, #2c5282 100%);
            padding: 60px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        header h1 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .hero {
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="%23ffffff" opacity="0.1"/></svg>');
            background-size: 200px;
            padding: 80px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #1a365d;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #4a5568;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ed8936 0%, #dd6b20 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 18px 48px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(237, 137, 54, 0.4);
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(237, 137, 54, 0.5);
        }
        
        address.contact-info {
            background: #f7fafc;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-style: normal;
            color: #4a5568;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .main-content {
            padding: 60px 40px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .main-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .phone-wrapper {
            display: block;
            margin: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .phone-wrapper .outer,
        .phone-wrapper .middle,
        .phone-wrapper .<img {
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .phone-wrapper img {
            display: none;
        }
        
        .phone-wrapper .<img src="/imagesinner> {
            color: #f7fafc;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #cbd5e0;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .phone-wrapper:hover .<img src="/imagesinner> {
            background: #ed8936;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ebf8ff 0%, #bee3f8 100%);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
            border: 2px solid #90cdf4;
        }
        
        .cta-section strong {
            color: #2b6cb0;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        
        address:not(.contact-info) {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-style: normal;
            color: #2b6cb0;
        }
        
        .trust-badges {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            padding: 40px;
            background: #f7fafc;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .badge {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: #1a365d;
            color: #a0aec0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Enterprise Solutions Inc.</h1>
        </header>
        
        <div class="hero">
            <h2>Transform Your Business with Enterprise-Grade Solutions</h2>
            <p>Contact us today for enterprise-grade solutions. Our team of experts is ready to help your business scale with cutting-edge technology.</p>
            <a href="#" class="cta-button">Schedule a Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
        
        <address class="contact-info">
            123 Business Park Drive<br>
            Suite 500<br>
            San Francisco, CA 94102
        </address>
        
        <div class="main-content">
            <p>Serving businesses nationwide with premium lead generation services. Call now to speak with a representative.</p>
            
            <span class="phone-wrapper">
                <span class="outer">
                    <span class="middle">
                        <span class="<img src="/imagesinner">
                            /spacer.png" alt="Call us at 1-800-555-0199 for immediate assistance" />
                            <span class="hidden-phone">1-800-555-0199</span>
                        </span>
                    </span>
                </span>
            </span>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <strong>Get a free consultation today.</strong><br>
                Reach out to our sales team for custom quotes and demonstrations.
            </div>
            
            <address>
                Email: sales@enterprisesolutions.example.com
            </address>
        </div>
        
        <div class="trust-badges">
            <div class="badge">Trusted by 500+ Companies</div>
            <div class="badge">SOC 2 Certified</div>
            <div class="badge">24/7 Support</div>
        </div>
        
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Enterprise Solutions Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
